  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed development would, by reason of its proximity to its boundaries, would appear as a cramped form of development which would be out of the character with the prevailing built form in the street scene, harmful to the character and appearance of the surrounding area contrary to Policies 7 and 26 of the Havering Local Plan, Emerson Park Policy Area Supplementary Planning Document 2009.",
